These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
City: marseilles, berlin, nizza, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person eating mango is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| City   | berlin  | marseilles     | nizza   | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, designer, photographer, doctor
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the designer##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the designer is on the left of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Job   | photographer    | designer      | freelancer | doctor |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, american, egyptian, japanese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the colombian is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the japanese##1
5. the egyptian is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Nationality         | colombian | japanese | egyptian   | american |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, potato, papaya, radish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person eating radish##1
2. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating apple##1
4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating radish##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | radish | potato | apple  | papaya      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

