.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, cycling, handball, water-polo
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Sport    | rugby       | water-polo | handball | cycling     |

