.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, blend, old-henry, game
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, mouse
1. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | game | old-henry | aristoff | blend |
| Pet           | fish      | goldfish | mouse | frog    |

