.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, indie, salsa
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, skateboard, airplane, roller
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | electronic | classical | salsa  |
| Transport           | airplane | van | roller       | skateboard |

