.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, rose, zinnia, orchid
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Flower         | zinnia | daisy      | rose | orchid |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

