.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, august, september
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, taxi, train, tram
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Birthday    | november | august  | march | september |
| Transport   | tram | train | taxi          | bus    |

