.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, magic-tricks, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, disco, r&b
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of disco##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | traveling  | fishing | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | disco | r&b           | d&b   |

