1. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is the person driving the roller##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Sport   | weightlifting      | soccer | swimming | badminton |
| Transport     | quad-bike | van    | subway  | roller |

