.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, mah-jongg, canasta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, family, scientific, spy
1. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Game      | billiard   | canasta | monopoly   | mah-jongg      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | spy      | family | scientific |

