.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
City: new-york, edinburgh, san-francisco, hamburg
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| City   | new-york | san-francisco | edinburgh | hamburg   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 